  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_0' aria-label=\" M/s Aristo Printers Pvt. Ltd. versus Commissioner of Trade Tax, Lucknow, U.P. pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('0','2025','2025_10_405_462','2025INSC1188'); ><font size='4'> <strong>M/S ARISTO PRINTERS PVT. LTD.<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>COMMISSIONER OF TRADE TAX, LUCKNOW, U.P. </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 10 S.C.R. 405</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 1188</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010004602025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : J.B. PARDIWALA<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, K.V. VISWANATHAN</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Issue arose whether tax can be levied u/s.3F of the Uttar Pradesh Trade Tax Act, 1948, on the ink and processing material used by the appellant in undertaking the printing work of lottery tickets. Headnotes&dagger; Uttar Pradesh Trade Tax Act, 1948 &ndash; ss.2(m), &ndash; Tax on the right to use any goods or goods involved in the execution of works contract &ndash; Appellant undertaking the printing work of lottery tickets &ndash; Levy of trade tax u/s.3F on the ink, chemical and processing material used by the appellant &ndash; Tribunal deleted the<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 07-10-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CIVIL APPEAL No. 703/2012</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Disposed off</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('0','2025','2025_10_405_462','2025INSC1188','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('0','2025','2025_10_405_462','2025INSC1188','H'); ><i class='fas fa-file-alt me-2'></i>HTML view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_flip('0','2025','2025_10_405_462','2025INSC1188');><i class='fas fa-book-open me-2' ></i>Flip view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_pdf('0','2025','2025_10_405_462','2025INSC1188','N'); ><i class='fas fa-file-pdf me-2'></i>PDF</a></div></div>",
